blog.name: thefearisoneself
blog.title: You know. Me, Chad of Camelot.
blog.description: Hello! Please call me Jir! While I reblog lots of things my art is all under my Moominvalley tag, please check it out! I'm a 21 year old girl with High functioning Autism from Canada. My current biggest fandom is Moomins with my favourite character being Snufkin. I am also a fan of Wander over Yonder, Star vs the Forces of Evil, Steven Universe, Ducktales, Undertale, Gravity Falls, the Adventure Zone, OK KO and We Bare Bears. If you have any questions or just want to tell me something, go right ahead, don't be afraid to ask! Just please nothing rude.

Okay so,

Snufkin with trombocytopenia (but a mild case- or not. Whichever you prefer).

He gets these random bruises and purpura and everyone gets shook whenever they touch them cause??? They don’t hurt?? Tf Snufkin.

He’s like chilling with Moomin on a chill day and has an itchy nose so he just itches one time anD A BIG ASS RED STREAM COMES OUT FOR A FEW SECONDS- and then it stops and you have to deal with the mess.

And when he falls badly Moomin just yeets him to Moominmamma so she can rush to fix the boy up cause that’s gonna bleed for hours.

Also just?? Waking up cause ya have a bloodnose, it’s a mood. Then you complain about your throay hurting because of all that nasty stuff ya swallowed.

Am I grumpy and making Snufkin deal with my shit. Yes

Me hand filthy with blud.
